			</font>
			<font face="Verdana" size="1"><b>
			Submited by:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:Dreamz725@aol.com">Seijuro Hiko</a></font> 
			<font face="Verdana" size="1">On:&nbsp;5/18/2000 1:05:33 PM</font></b>
			<td nowrap bgcolor="#808080" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_silver.gif" align="right">
				<font face="Verdana" size="1"><b>Rank:&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>	
				<font face="Verdana" size="1">worst</font>
				<b><a href="javascript:openWindow(1,137785);"><font face="Verdana" size="1" >1</font></a></b>
				<b><a href="javascript:openWindow(2,137785);"><font face="Verdana" size="1" >2</font></a></b>
