				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I've found out that you turn in 3 platinum pieces to the erudite guy behind the named orc in South Ro.<BR>
Also, another good way to raise faction with the Temple of Solusek Ro:<BR>
In Castle Mistmoore, there is a graveyard with a small house in the middle of it. Inside the house there is a flower lying on a coffin. Pick up the flower, and go behind the house and give it to a Ssynthi (not sure on spelling). This will raise your faction with the Temple of Sol Ro, and the flower respawns very quickly. Too bad its lore though. Good luck.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
